text: Jang Yong-ho (born April 4, 1976) is a South Korean archer. Yong-ho competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, 2000 Summer Olympics and the 2004 Summer Olympics.Jang Yong-Ho ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea
